{
  "stem": "3685.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In Shabbat we used to take [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, from shul, it was always some poor people which were looking for a meal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So every Friday night, that was a custom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody else-- some-- everybody else took-- and it-- it's an Hebrew called [HEBREW], or a poor man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we used to come in and feed him with the dinner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father was-- in the summer-- he worked in the fields.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we also had hired help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a good general store, like I said before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were well off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was from 1919 till-- till-- till the-- the Holocaust-- from 1919.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my-- my-- my father was born in 1919.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was married in 1919, and he came to Stremilcze.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then where he set up-- and he made-- and he start doing business there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my grandmother and my grandfather was there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the non-Jews?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fair, fair, because you see, we had-- there was another Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a store also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rest were more or less-- it was one guy-- he was-- it was one-- mostly were farmers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, and some were tradesmen only.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they were buying and selling stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that-- that's all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the rest of the-- the community-- all were farmers-- all farmers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't say-- I wouldn't say that there was, actually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, in 1936, '37, where after Hitler came to power in Germany, that's when we felt the anti-Semitism start blowing up-- blowing out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, in mainly in the big cities like Lemberg, that was there, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a different-- that's where it were, the anti-Semitism was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in-- in the little-- in my little town, I didn't really feel it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
